quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,238,( mslmano ) sab namazain khasosan beech ki namaz ( yani namaz asar ) poooray iltazam ke sath ada karte raho. aur khuda ke agay adab se kharray raha karo
  2,239,agar tum khauf ki haalat mein ho to payaday ya sawaar ( jis haal mein ho namaz parh lau ) phir jab aman ( wa itmenaan ) hojaye to jis tareeq se khuda ne tum ko sikhaya hai jo tum pehlay nahi jantay they khuda ko yaad karo
  2,240,aur jo log tum mein se mrjayin aur aurtain chore jayen woh apni aurton ke haq mein wasiyat krjayin ke un ko aik saal taq kharch diya jaye aur ghar se nah nikaali jayen. haan agar woh khud ghar se nikal jayen aur apne haq mein pasandeeda kaam ( yani nikah ) karlen to tum par kuch gunah nahi. aur khuda zabardast hikmat wala hai
  2,241,aur mutalqa aurton ko bhi dastoor ke mutabiq nan o nfqh dena chahiye parhaiz garon par ( yeh bhi ) haq hai
  2,242,isi terhan khuda apne ehkaam tumahray liye bayan farmata hai taakay tum samjhoo
  2,243,bhala tum ne un logon ko nahi dekha jo ( shumaar mein ) hazaron hi they aur mout ke dar se apne gharon se nikal bhage they. to khuda ne un ko hukum diya ke marjao. phir un ko zindah bhi kardiya. kuch shak nahi ke khuda logon par meharbani rakhta hai. lekin aksar log shukar nahi karte
  2,244,aur ( mslmano ) khuda ki raah mein jehaad karo aur jaan rakho ke khuda ( sab kuch ) jaanta hai
  2,245,koi hai ke khuda ko qarz husna day ke woh is ke badlay is ko kayi hissay ziyada day ga. aur khuda hi rozi ko tang karta aur ( wohi usay ) kushadah karta hai. aur tum isi ki taraf lout kar jao ge
